<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VEXEL X | Unknown Rank</title>
    <style>
        /* إعدادات الخلفية والخطوط */
        body {
            background-color: #0a0a0a;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* الحاوية الرئيسية */
        .main-card {
            background: rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.8);
            padding: 60px 40px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(0, 150, 255, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #00a2ff;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 162, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .rank-tag {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #b0b0b0;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #000000;
            padding: 18px 45px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #00a2ff;
            color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 162, 255, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .status-container {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #444;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="main-card">
        <div class="rank-tag">[ ACCESS GRANTED: UNKNOWN RANK ]</div>
        <h1>VEXEL X</h1>
        <p>Experience the most advanced AI engine. High-velocity image generation, 4s cinematic videos, and persistent neural memory.</p>
        
        <a href="https://link.prod.sekai.chat/GOskSM" class="btn">Launch Engine</a>

        <div class="status-container">
            SYSTEM STATUS: OPERATIONAL | DEVELOPER: ZAKARIA
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>

